survey_response.review_text: DR Anjali was introduced to us for our baby’s (1 month old) vaccination and we observed a well organised health care in terms of appointments, meeting with doctor, making baby comfortable at clinic to treat the baby and also makes us more comfortable in terms of clarifying our never ending clarifications. Doctor is friendly in nature and gives satisfying explanations related to our baby care and health. We are happy and feel safe to be able to get our health care f I’m the clinic. Highly recommend the clinic Kids Ecare clinic, Kattupakkam.

We Love how amazing this young doctor and her staff is..! They always follow up with us and call to remind us about our appointments. For me its all about convenience and they are always flexible to fit time around my schedule! If we needed to see her same day they make time..
She always been calm and reassuring which is what I need. He listens and makes decisions with you. It feels so nice to know that I can trust her word. She was great with my three year old too!  my baby boy love her..!! 

Ethical practise.. Avoiding unnecessary supplements or antibiotics..which I found very different from others..

Doc..You have shown your kindness and incredible knowledge through your ongoing treatment. You never take a parent's concern lightly, and treat our son with great respect for his privacy and needs as well. You have a Godly touch, and we appreciate you and your staff very much..

We take our 4.5 year old daughter whenever she is not well to Kid-e-clinic in Katupakkam bus stop.
Dr.Anjali is very patient and gets all details to diagonize the problem and provides detailed explanation of the same with a splendid course of action till its resolved.She suggests natural remedies with minimal dosage of medicines only based on the severity of the illness. She takes a lot of effort to explain in detail any queries from parents till we get convinced.She remembers the details and would follow up on the status of the recuperation . She makes the child very much comfortable and is very passionate .
Definitely recommended to all from Poonamallee to Porur area residents and other parts of Chennai city too . All types of vaccinations and medicines are available at the clinic which is very advanageous.

She doesn't recommend unwanted medicine. She suggests natural way to treat the issue first. She is a good doctor whom I can trust my child with. Very friendly and listens to our questions. Also, we get remainder call for vaccination which is very helpful.
